{"tid":1102000,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解落雨唔可以嗌炒蛋？","createTime":"2019-04-11T11:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T12:13:47.000Z","uid":6766,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"185b88a8f2fc74165e0a2bc02704ce3b2a8c2997","tid":1102000,"uid":6766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"話說今日lunch 成班同事去食飯<br />\n<br />\n咁啱去到間餐廳就開始落大雨 好彩有帶遮<br />\n<br />\n幾日無食蛋 見到有道叉燒煎蛋 但我又唔想食煎蛋 <br />\n<br />\n咪問佢可唔可以轉做炒蛋 <br />\n<br />\n點知個侍應聽完 大大聲當住其他食客面前屌我落雨炒蛋係咪想玩野 <br />\n<br />\n成間餐廳嘅人都望住我笑 最大鑊係班同事到收工果刻都笑緊 話我無常識 仲要搞到今日老細經過我個位都陰陰咀笑 <br />\n<br />\n到底有無人可以話我知點解落雨唔嗌得炒蛋？ 聽日都唔知點面對班同事好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c15cd237548d66bf826183c7733b13c347c9ef","tid":1102000,"uid":19528,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:53:41.000Z","msg":"見你咁白癡就答下你啦<br />\n<br />\n眾所週知 蛋有不同煮法 但最正宗同最原始既蛋就一定係太陽蛋 顧名思義 呢隻係要太陽下先整到既蛋 利用太陽既熱力，整熟隻蛋<br />\n<br />\n但之後陸陸續續有其他蛋煮法出現 好似炒，蒸等等<br />\n<br />\n炒蛋要用滾油，落雨會有水花 水同油因為磁通量完全唔同 兩者因為粒子性質唔同而彈開 又稱彈油 普通人一掂到輕則毀容，重則甩皮 風險極高 所以一般餐廳都唔會比員工以身犯險落雨去煮呢道菜<br />\n<br />\n有雨落炒蛋供應既餐廳只有少數 而且細佬有幸食過一次<br />\n個種回甘真係難以忘懷..."},{"pid":"283efef292384b6f17dd516f932a6bc662027594","tid":1102000,"uid":49222,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩"},{"pid":"02d794b34f5b7dfcf0a3cd8a8bb1a7735dcadc13","tid":1102000,"uid":6766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"283efef292384b6f17dd516f932a6bc662027594","tid":1102000,"uid":49222,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"我知我煩 但我google 過同埋上網揾過啲舊post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但入面太多假膠 無一個真正答案 所以好想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0dc479d62e5449a9266f1e9fe5947b482341f4","tid":1102000,"uid":153503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"落雨仲叫炒蛋 你都痴線既 咁危險 想收買人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2c1cc4ce02a9601fb1d2b74717810eff300e0a","tid":1102000,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02d794b34f5b7dfcf0a3cd8a8bb1a7735dcadc13","tid":1102000,"uid":6766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"283efef292384b6f17dd516f932a6bc662027594","tid":1102000,"uid":49222,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"我知我煩 但我google 過同埋上網揾過啲舊post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但入面太多假膠 無一個真正答案 所以好想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"樓主先假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba0dfd6a63e8767a55149c7d52446b55c4a73cd","tid":1102000,"uid":6766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bf2c1cc4ce02a9601fb1d2b74717810eff300e0a","tid":1102000,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02d794b34f5b7dfcf0a3cd8a8bb1a7735dcadc13","tid":1102000,"uid":6766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"283efef292384b6f17dd516f932a6bc662027594","tid":1102000,"uid":49222,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"我知我煩 但我google 過同埋上網揾過啲舊post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h